name: TreeBag_addTest
description: Unit tests for the add method of the TreeBag class.

test_cases.name: testAddWithComparableObject
test_cases.description: Tests the add method of TreeBag with a comparable object (String).

test_cases.name: testAddWithNonComparableObjectAndNoComparator
test_cases.description: Tests the add method of TreeBag with a non-comparable object and no custom comparator, expecting an IllegalArgumentException.

test_cases.name: testAddWithNonComparableObjectAndCustomComparator
test_cases.description: Tests the add method of TreeBag with a non-comparable object and a custom comparator.
